<view class="page" wx:if="{{summary}}">
  <view class="section privacy-head">
    <view class="privacy-kicker">LOCAL-FIRST DATA</view>
    <view class="title">你的数据，由你控制。</view>
    <view class="subtitle">当前版本不要求登录，个人规划资料主要保存在这台设备的微信本地存储中。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section local-boundary-card">
    <view class="privacy-kicker dark">LOCAL DATA · {{releaseInfo.version}}</view>
    <view class="panel-title">本机数据边界</view>
    <view class="boundary-summary">{{releaseInfo.target}} · {{releaseInfo.dataMode}}</view>
    <view class="boundary-list">
      <view wx:for="{{localBoundaries}}" wx:key="mark" class="boundary-row">
        <view class="boundary-mark">{{item.mark}}</view>
        <view>
          <view class="boundary-title">{{item.title}}</view>
          <view class="boundary-copy">{{item.copy}}</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section panel">
    <view class="panel-title">本机数据概览</view>
    <view class="summary-grid">
      <view class="summary-item"><view class="summary-value">{{summary.favoriteCount}}</view><view class="summary-label">收藏</view></view>
      <view class="summary-item"><view class="summary-value">{{summary.completedCount}}</view><view class="summary-label">已修记录</view></view>
      <view class="summary-item"><view class="summary-value">{{summary.studyPlanCount}}</view><view class="summary-label">计划课程</view></view>
      <view class="summary-item"><view class="summary-value">{{summary.noteCount}}</view><view class="summary-label">课程笔记</view></view>
    </view>
    <view class="profile-state">{{summary.hasProfile ? '已保存学校与专业资料' : '尚未保存学校与专业资料'}}</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section flow-card">
    <view class="flow-title">数据如何流动</view>
    <view class="flow-row">
      <view class="flow-mark local">本机</view>
      <view><view class="flow-name">资料、收藏、Study Plan、笔记</view><view class="flow-copy">保存在微信本地存储；不会自动同步到云端或其他设备。</view></view>
    </view>
    <view class="flow-row">
      <view class="flow-mark api">查询</view>
      <view><view class="flow-name">课程查询与毕业检查</view><view class="flow-copy">{{dataStatus.runtime.apiEnabled ? '开发版可能连接本机服务；查询只包含筛选条件、专业、培养年份和课程标识，不包含姓名或课程笔记。' : '体验版与正式版直接读取离线数据；课程笔记不会上传。'}}</view></view>
    </view>
    <view class="flow-row">
      <view class="flow-mark copy">复制</view>
      <view><view class="flow-name">文本备份</view><view class="flow-copy">只有你点击“复制备份”时，数据才会写入系统剪贴板。</view></view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section action-card">
    <view class="panel-title">带走或删除数据</view>
    <view class="action-copy">换手机、重装微信或清除前，先复制文本备份。恢复时不会联网，只会写回这台设备的本地存储。</view>
    <view class="backup-button" bindtap="copyBackup">复制完整备份</view>
    <view class="restore-button" bindtap="restoreBackup">从剪贴板恢复</view>
    <view class="delete-button" bindtap="clearAllData">清除全部本机数据</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section legal-note">这是当前版本的产品数据说明，不替代小程序正式发布时需要配置的平台隐私保护指引；发布前仍需要在微信公众平台完成隐私与类目配置。</view>
</view>
